snippet.title: Amber Heard Lays A Turd, Grace Randolph BRUTALLY Honest About Birds Of Prey - TC Talk Podcast 001
snippet.description:
On this debut episode of The TC Talk Podcast I discuss the early Birds Of Prey reactions, Amber Heard being absolutely batshit crazy, and Sebastian Stan deciding to talk back to the mouse aka Disney.

Time Stamps:

1:07 Intro
6:08 Sponsors
8:54 Birds Of Prey Early Reactions
23:31 Sebastian Stan Talks Back To Disney
28:13 Amber Heard Lays A Turd
39:05 Q & A
52:14 One Final Thought
